name: EvolveAI
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.

description.en: We are the first on both socials to create these Bots, and we have an insane impact. Being the first  gave us the headstart and alowed for our massive growth and popularity. Within the first 10 days of launch, our bot had been active in over 4,000 groups and has been used over 1,000,000 times. From crypto users to non-crypto people, everyone uses it in their daily routine. Due to the nature of telegram and twitter, users are able to directly share their outputs instantly and without the need to save replies.
